{"tid":324380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人既語言應該叫「香港話」，「港語」","createTime":"2017-07-16T11:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T23:30:35.000Z","uid":33307,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9044f32bc932528dff7497a234ab61cccaa512a6","tid":324380,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:44:49.000Z","msg":"廣東話根本唔岩用<br />\n你試下去同廣州人溝通<br />\n對方只係明五成<br />\n港語又英文又剩<br />\n根本就係唔同語言<br />\n至多你話係類似語言<br />\n唔信你去百度出個post<br />\n冇人明你講咩<br />\n所以應該叫香港話，港語"},{"pid":"fc8a8cd3c59eefdc58cd9fa98e821354812f555b","tid":324380,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:45:33.000Z","msg":"岩呀"},{"pid":"0eb631a178e34f911a49a13da061c76b7e51dead","tid":324380,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩呀</blockquote><br />\n根本語氣，講法都唔同"},{"pid":"aee6778822c86d3ae5df1f82a66e99e79624410b","tid":324380,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩呀</blockquote><br />\n根本語氣，講法都唔同</blockquote><br />\n港式廣東話<br />\n就好似美國都有English(US)"},{"pid":"0248829e56bd5dde11cc6e0eef50e724d51c8eef","tid":324380,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩呀</blockquote><br />\n根本語氣，講法都唔同</blockquote><br />\n港式廣東話<br />\n就好似美國都有English(US)</blockquote><br />\n夾集英文都係廣東話？發文係咪法式廣東話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704357a3069654063636cf389c7178053c302fa0","tid":324380,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩呀</blockquote><br />\n根本語氣，講法都唔同</blockquote><br />\n港式廣東話<br />\n就好似美國都有English(US)</blockquote><br />\n夾集英文都係廣東話？發文係咪法式廣東話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法文"},{"pid":"